    "created_at": "2016-12-18T01:29:47Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-12-18T01:29:47Z",
    "body": "I'm actually super not into other apps being able to reach into Slack and nerf its performance, because people won't make the connection that \"I enabled this app => Slack is slower\", they'll just think Slack is slow and blame us.\r\n\r\nInstead of abusing accessibility APIs for things that aren't accessibility, we should make an API to actually get the information directly without sending thousands of thousands of accessibility events, 99.9% of which are ignored"
  },
