    "updated_at": "2017-04-06T22:27:01Z",
    "body": "We use a WebDriver tool for automation scripts that uses accessibility on macOS. It's called [AppiumForMac](https://github.com/appium/appium-for-mac). It works for all elements of our native apps, and the menu bar for our Electron app. It would be great to have a non-VoiceOver enabler for Electron window contents."
